    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As a hind let loose is Naphtali"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Giving beautiful words from his mouth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Full of grace, receiving all God's blessings,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Possessing both the sea and the south."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let the high gospel be proclaimed,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With the life of Christ outpoured;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Boldly go, the lands and peoples claim"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By the pow'r promised of the Lord."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lo, the world is full of hungry souls,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Only Christ has the surplus to feed;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Quickly rise！ Throw open Joseph's storehouse,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Lord calls us to fill all their need."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Says the Lord, Whom ~ shall I send;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And ~ who will go for Us?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We respond: Lord, Here am I; send me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All Your will do accomplish thus."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Judah's lion conquers every foe,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To establish His kingdom of worth;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ruler's staff and scepter ne'er shall leave him"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till Shiloh comes and peace fills the earth."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We'll the Lord's victory display,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Pow'r of darkness vanquishing;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus we'll reign in life, as Spirit leads,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To all nations, His blessing bring."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Joseph is a fruitful bough indeed,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bearing fruit by the fount without end;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nothing hinders this life's reproduction;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As o'er the wall his branches extend."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the Lord constantly abide,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In His flow of life divine;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In all things, let Christ be magnified;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bear new fruit; let His virtues shine."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Issachar, between the sheepfolds lies—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Gains the good land, at rest in his lot;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In his tents made glad, he bows his shoulder,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And offers pleasing tribute to God."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ the good land we must enjoy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Drop religion utterly;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the church, as members functioning,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Build His Body organically."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Benjamin, beloved of the Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Like a ravenous wolf for the fight,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Foe destroys, at morn the prey devouring,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dividing spoil in triumph at night."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ's belov'd, with Him we'd abide;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Gladsome shelter, rest, obtain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God and man forever satisfied—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let's press forward, this goal attain!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
